<tr><td>
    <h3 align=center id=qname>Inert Potion</h3><hr size=1>
	 <table width=100% cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 border=0>
	 <tr><td valign=top>
	 <table cellpadding=1 cellspacing=1 border=0 align=left>
	 <tr><td><b>Starts in:</b></td><td><a href='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Odus/Erudin.htm'>Erudin</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Who:</b></td><td><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=579>Toresian Fhabel</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Rating:</b></td><td>Good (4.25)</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Estimated Time:</b></td><td>1 hour</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Minimum Level:</b></td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td><b>Best Class:</b></td><td>All</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Factions Raised:</b><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=54">Carson McCabe</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=29">Coalition of Trade Folk</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=30">Coalition of Tradefolk Illegal</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=96">Corrupt Qeynos Guards</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=12">Crimson Hands</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=31">Freeport Militia</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Factions Lowered:</b></span><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=15">High Counsel of Erudin</a></li><li><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=17">High Guard of Erudin</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Additional Zones:</b></span><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Qeynos.htm>Qeynos North</a></li><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Qeynos.htm>Qeynos South</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Related Creatures:</b></span><li>Gate Bandit</li><li><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=537>Slansin</a></li></ul></td></tr></td></tr></table>On the third floor of the castle, Toresian Fhabel is waiting for someone to take an inert potion down to Vials of Vitality, on the first floor of the castle, and give it to Slansin.  There are two people who you can give the potion to.  Some times the correct person (with a single name, not a surname) 'spawns' in the shop and if you hand the bottle to him, you gain with several Erudin Factions. Usually (it may now be always) if you run this quest then "A Gate Bandit", [now also named Slansin?] will spawn in place of the person you are supposed to give the bottle to.  If you hand the bottle to the bandit, the following factions go up:  Coalition of Trade Folk Ill, Coalition of Tradefolk, Carson McCabe, Corrupt Qeynos Guards and The Freeport Militia.  The best part of these faction changes is that it raises lots of hard to raise factions without lowering any others.  You can do this over and over again to improve all these factions at once.  This bandit is about L10 or 11, and it is possible that killing him starts a new quest by talking to one of the NPC's in the shop.  Also, the bandit tells you that a friend will avenge his death [of course that is standard language], and if you take the boat to Qeynos after doing the quest, a guard will sometimes attack you when you get off.  I don't know what happens if you defeat the guard. </td></tr>
	 <tr><td id=rt valign=top>Reward(s):</td></tr>
	 <tr><td valign=top><li>Lots of (nice) faction</li></td></tr>
	 <tr><td colspan=2 align=center>Last modified on Sat Jun 24 09:27:50 2000</td></tr>
	 <tr><td colspan=2 align=center>36 people have rated this quest</td></tr>
	 <tr><td colspan=2 align=center><a href="mailto:AllaKhazam@AllaKhazam.com?Subject=Correction for Inert Potion&body=On the page http://everquest.allakhazam.com//quest.html?quest=141

">Send a Correction</a></td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
