	   <tr><td colspan=2>Toresian Fhabel is of the CraftKeepers faction. To gain faction with him, go to Toxxulia Forest and camp Elial Brook. It took me exactly 20 kills to go from dubious to amiable for my DE (60 CHA).<br><br>Slansin is of the CoalitionOfTheTradesFolkIll faction (Freeport Rogues). To gain faction with him, get a truckload of Kiola Nuts and Water Flasks (Sister Island in OOT) and give them to Tumpy Irontoe in North Kaladim to make Tumpy Tonics. Once you get the tonics, give them to Groflah Steadirt in Seafarer's Roost in East Freeport. 8 stacks got me from scowl (as a DE, I did the Halfling Bandage quest) to amiable.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
